import React from 'react'; import { Globe, LayoutDashboard, Plane, AlertTriangle, RefreshCw, FileText, Settings, HelpCircle } from 'lucide-react'; // Translations for sidebar const translations = { en: { analysis: 'Analysis', globe: 'Globe View', overview: 'Overview', airlines: 'Airlines', priority: 'Priority Analysis', systemic: 'Systemic Cases', legal: 'Legal Summary', settings: 'Settings', configuration: 'Configuration', help: 'Help & Docs', semester: 'Semester', language: 'Language', }, de: { analysis: 'Analyse', globe: 'Globus-Ansicht', overview: 'Übersicht', airlines: 'Fluggesellschaften', priority: 'Prioritätsanalyse', systemic: 'Systemische Fälle', legal: 'Rechtliche Zusammenfassung', settings: 'Einstellungen', configuration: 'Konfiguration', help: 'Hilfe & Docs', semester: 'Semester', language: 'Sprache', }, fr: { analysis: 'Analyse', globe: 'Vue Globe', overview: 'Aperçu', airlines: 'Compagnies Aériennes', priority: 'Analyse des Priorités', systemic: 'Cas Systémiques', legal: 'Résumé Juridique', settings: 'Paramètres', configuration: 'Configuration', help: 'Aide & Docs', semester: 'Semestre', language: 'Langue', }, }; const semesters = [ { value: '2024-H2', label: '2024 H2 (Jul-Dec)' }, { value: '2024-H1', label: '2024 H1 (Jan-Jun)' }, { value: '2023-H2', label: '2023 H2 (Jul-Dec)' }, { value: '2023-H1', label: '2023 H1 (Jan-Jun)' }, { value: '2022-H2', label: '2022 H2 (Jul-Dec)' }, ]; const Sidebar = ({ activeTab, setActiveTab, language, setLanguage, semester, setSemester, priorityCount = 5, systemicCount = 3 }) => { const t = translations[language] || translations.en; const navItems = [ { id: 'globe', icon: Globe, label: t.globe }, { id: 'overview', icon: LayoutDashboard, label: t.overview }, { id: 'airlines', icon: Plane, label: t.airlines }, { id: 'priority', icon: AlertTriangle, label: t.priority, badge: { count: priorityCount, type: 'danger' } }, { id: 'systemic', icon: RefreshCw, label: t.systemic, badge: { count: systemicCount, type: 'warning' } }, { id: 'legal', icon: FileText, label: t.legal }, ]; return (
{/* Logo */}
✈️
CASA
Reporting Dashboard
{/* Semester Selector */}
{t.semester}
{/* Navigation */}
{t.analysis}
{navItems.map((item) => (
setActiveTab(item.id)} >
{item.label} {item.badge && ( {item.badge.count} )}
))}
{/* Settings Section */}
{t.settings}
{t.configuration}
{t.help}
{/* Language Selector */}
{t.language}
); }; export default Sidebar;
